	<region id="editorData">
		<node id="editorData">
			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="1. Enter &quot;spawnItem UNI_S_DebugBook_31ee023c-d151-40f6-917e-84066772783b&quot; into ReCon to spawn the DebugBook&#xD;&#xA;2. Use the DebugBook to travel to ACT1: Crash Site&#xD;&#xA;3. Enter &quot;goto -452.25, 13.51, -381.75&quot; into ReCon to travel into the Blighted Village smithy&#xD;&#xA;4. Activate the Melting Furnace&#xD;&#xA;5. Activate the Blacksmith's Bellows&#xD;&#xA;6. Enter &quot;create QUEST_FOR_SussurBark&quot; into ReCon to spawn the Sussur Tree Bark&#xD;&#xA;7 Enter &quot;create WPN_Dagger&quot; into ReCon to spawn a dagger in your inventory&#xD;&#xA;8. Use the Melting Furnace to combine the Sussur Bark with the Melting Furnace&#xD;&#xA;9. Exit and re-enter the Melting Furnace crafting menu&#xD;&#xA;10. Add the 'Dagger' to the crafting menu" />
			<attribute id="needLayout" type="bool" value="False" />
			<attribute id="nextNodeId" type="uint32" value="410" />
			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="The player has all the ingredients and fires up the furnace to make their masterwork.This is all narration; narration needed as most of this scene will likely not be visually communicative." />
			<children>
				<node id="defaultAttitudes">
